  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A funeral in the open ocean. Maximum release (8 seconds) with cave body at 0.75 feedback creates notes that dissolve into resonant echoes long after release. Bio exciter at low rate (0.02 Hz) provides rare, solemn bioluminescent flickers — mourners holding lanterns in the dark water. Filter cutoff at 250 Hz with low resonance creates a muted, grieving tone. Every note is a goodbye that takes eight seconds to finish.",
