  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OCEANDEEP — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": ["Truth 6: The Release Cathedral at Golden Ratio", "Verse: The Depth Column — Deep Zone"],
    "revelation": "Tempora spoke: release at 8.0 seconds — the maximum — means the envelope takes longer to close than most musical phrases. The note outlives the intention that created it. At this timescale, monophonic legato creates a continuous requiem — each new note inherits the dying breath of the last through the envelope overlap.",
    "god": "Tempora",
    "flock_note": "The Ear heard the eight-second tail merge with the cave body resonance: the comb filter sustains the pitch memory while the envelope fades. The sound remembers the note after the note has gone. The Breath confirmed: bioRate 0.02 Hz means one bioluminescent flicker every 50 seconds — rare enough to feel like an event, not a pattern.",
    "diagnosis": "This sound was a bass with long release. It is now a requiem — each note a mourner, each release a farewell, each bio flicker a candle in the deep."
  },
